data.description: Freshly updated, and so cute & clean! Lovely single level home on a LARGE corner lot. Updates include new interior/exterior paint, new flooring, as well as new kitchen tile backsplash and floating shelves. Nice open floor plan that flows well from living to dining and kitchen. Access to the back yard from the dining, bedroom, and utility room. Main bath is nice sized plus a 1/2 bath off utility room. Large, fully fenced yard with irrigation well. Separate 10'x20' "man cave" or "she shed" with new underground power, insulation, and cooling.  Attached garage, alley access, & great off street parking. Lovely front patio. This single level home with an extra large corner lot is move-in ready!
